        "text": "Alternatively, the Lamb Oseen [10, 18] or Newman [17] vortex can be fitted to the data. These are also written in terms of Vs,max and rc, but the radial distribution function is different and a factor a of an exponential function defines the shape. Expanding the parameter a to the inclusion of the vortex age v, the Hamel Oseen [5] model can be used as well.",
